metadata.name: KASPAROV x TOPALOV (1999)
metadata.description:
"Kasparov vs. Topalov is everything a chess game should be, a ferocious fight with brilliance from both players, numerous tactical themes, and a king hunt that drives the king all the way from one side of the board to the other!" /Chess.com/

The placement of figures are based on the famous battle of 1999. 

Digital work, 5700 x 5700 px
